snippet.title: Ground Zero - Steam Page Mini Trailer - Search "Ground Zero" on Steam and wishlist!
snippet.description:
This is the mini-trailer from our now active Steam page, which is now up and ready for wishlists!

Please go to steam, search for Ground Zero and hit the wishlist button, thanks!

(Youtube doesn't yet allow embedded links until we reach a subscriber milestone)
